{"tid":1893570,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"【求助】CORSAIR iCUE","createTime":"2020-02-23T10:50:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-23T10:50:51.000Z","uid":39352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f72f07660fa508cb630d8717323c8c54600b49a7","tid":1893570,"uid":39352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T10:50:51.000Z","msg":"跪地求助<br />\n用開CORSAIR 鍵盤~之前裝左iCUE 但突然無法UPDATE到最新版本<br />\n然後諗住刪左佢再裝個新版本<br />\n跟住裝新版本個陣就唔比我裝 話我已經有舊版本係到<br />\n咁我之後就去CORSAIR 官網搵解決方法<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://help.corsair.com/hc/en-us/articles/360025166712-Perform-a-clean-reinstallation-of-the-Corsair-Utility-Engine-iCUE-\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhelp.corsair.com%2Fhc%2Fen-us%2Farticles%2F360025166712-Perform-a-clean-reinstallation-of-the-Corsair-Utility-Engine-iCUE-&d=c0FEOXRBadflfKsXjMdAys2proQWM4oxojYLcFbEfDU%3D&h=9108a7e9\" target=\"_blank\">https://help.corsair.com/hc/en-us/articles/360025166712-Perform-a-clean-reinstallation-of-the-Corsair-Utility-Engine-iCUE-</a><br />\n<br />\n跟住佢做左3次都仲係裝唔到 請問有無巴打可以幫幫手<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eb1L9Te.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Feb1L9Te.png&h=3e7fd483&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}